{"word":"G210 - ἄκων - ákōn - ak'-ohn - Against the will","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄκων</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ákōn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ak'-ohn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Against the will</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"உற்சாகமில்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"not of one's own will, unwilling"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G1635 - ἑκών - hekṓn - hek-own'/1635\">G1635</a>; <i>unwilling:</i> - against the will.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1595/1595\">G1595</a>, <a href=\"#/G210/210\">G210</a>"}]}